[User Routine     ] : SD_SO_SET_PARTNER
[User Routine Text] :
/SAPDMC/LSRATT                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER                   000     000                                                                                                0101WANG.FANG   20230425
/SAPDMC/LSRTXT                1BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0001* Eigene Routine
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0002FORM ur_sd_so_set_partner
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0003     USING i_kunnr
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0004              i_vkorg
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0005              i_vtweg
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0006              i_spart
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0007  CHANGING ct_partner TYPE wiso_t_parnr.
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0008
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0009  DATA:lt_knvp TYPE TABLE OF knvp .
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0010
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0011  CLEAR ct_partner[].
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0012  CHECK i_kunnr IS NOT INITIAL.
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0013  i_kunnr = |{ i_kunnr ALPHA = IN }|.
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0014
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0015
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0016  SELECT *
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0017    INTO TABLE lt_knvp
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0018    FROM knvp
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0019  WHERE kunnr = i_kunnr
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0020  AND vkorg = i_vkorg
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0021  AND vtweg = i_vtweg
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0022  AND spart = i_spart.
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0023
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0024  LOOP AT lt_knvp INTO DATA(ls_knvp).
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0025    APPEND VALUE #(
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0026    partn_role = ls_knvp-parvw
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0027    partn_numb = ls_knvp-kunn2
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0028    ) TO ct_partner.
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0029  ENDLOOP.
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0030
/SAPDMC/LSRCOD                BATCH          URSD_SO_SET_PARTNER             0031ENDFORM.
